OL,3,CLondon's congestion charge to rise -
OL,4,Cwhat could you be paying?
OL,6,FMotorists in central London are set to
OL,7,Fbe hit with an-inflation busting 20%
OL,8,Fhike in the daily Congestion Charge.
OL,10,FLabour mayor Sadiq Khan is planning to
OL,11,Fincrease the charge from #15 to #18
OL,12,Fand scrap the exemption for electric
OL,13,Fvehicles (EVs).
OL,15,FHe also wants to look at increasing
OL,16,Fthe charge every 12 months in line
OL,17,Fwith the annual rise in bus, tube and
OL,18,Ftrain fares.
