OL,3,CLondon's congestion charge to rise -
OL,4,Cwhat could you be paying?
OL,6,FResidents of the congestion zone will
OL,7,Fcontinue to benefit from a 90%
OL,8,Fdiscount but from March 2027 new
OL,9,Fapplications will only be accepted
OL,10,Ffrom EV drivers.
OL,12,FAnyone moving to central London with a
OL,13,Fpetrol, diesel or hybrid will pay full
OL,14,Fprice.
OL,16,FThe C Charge last went up from #11.50
OL,17,Fto #15.00 in June 2020 during the
OL,18,FCovid outbreak.
