OL,3,CLondon's congestion charge to rise -
OL,4,Cwhat could you be paying?
OL,6,FThe Congestion Charge was introduced
OL,7,Fin 2003 by London's first mayor, Ken
OL,8,FLivingstone. The daily fee was #5.00.
OL,10,FDeputy Mayor for Transport Seb Dance
OL,11,Fsaid: "Sticking to the status quo
OL,12,Fwould see around 2,200 more vehicles
OL,13,Fusing the congestion charging zone on
OL,14,Fan average weekday next year.
